vodozemac
  Copyright 2021-2024 The Matrix.org Foundation C.I.C.
  Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
  Source: https://github.com/matrix-org/vodozemac

  adapt-e2e-core vendors a pinned fork of vodozemac 0.10.0 under
  `vendor/vodozemac/`. Modifications by adapt-toolkit (full ledger in PATCH.md):
    - an additive `*_with_rng` entropy-injection API that threads a
      caller-supplied CSPRNG through the Olm key-generation paths (proposed
      upstream as matrix-org/vodozemac#379);
    - feature-gating of the OS-RNG default methods and the non-Olm engines behind
      `std-rng`, so the default build links no `getrandom`/`OsRng`;
    - `#![no_std]` + `alloc` support for bare-metal targets.
  The original audited code paths are unchanged.

